text: Dalbergia candenatensis is a species of liana, with the Vietnamese name trắc một hột (or me nước). It is now placed in the subfamily Faboideae and tribe Dalbergieae; no subspecies are listed in the Catalogue of Life. == References == Sanjappa,M., 1992 Legumes of India.
